<div id="content_wrapper" class="longformpage">
	<!-- <h2></h2> -->
			<div class="longform post_img fullwidth">
			<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/beachblanketbingo-copy.jpg" alt="" class="entry_post"/>
		</div>
				<h1>The Ultimate Summer 2025 Reading List</h1>
		<h2>Sun, Fun, Math, and Counting</h2>
    <div class="inner">
		<div class="post_header_wrapper">
    				</div>
				<div class="author_info" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
			<div class="author_name">By&nbsp;<a href="https://lithub.com/author/emily-temple/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Emily&nbsp;Temple</span></a></div>
			<div class="author_hr"><hr/></div>
			<div class="publish_date">June 12, 2025</div>
		</div>
		<div class="social_links">
						<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=lithub&text=The+Ultimate+Summer+2025+Reading+List&url=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthe-ultimate-summer-2025-reading-list%2F"><span class="social_twitter"></span></a>
			<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthe-ultimate-summer-2025-reading-list%2F&t=The+Ultimate+Summer+2025+Reading+List"><span class="social_facebook"></span></a>
					</div>
    <div class="inner">
    	<!-- Begin main content -->
    	<div class="inner_wrapper fullwidth">
    			
										<!-- Begin each blog post -->
						<div class="post_wrapper" style="padding-top:0;">
							<div class="post_inner_wrapper">
						    	<div class="post_wrapper_inner">
										<div class="inner_wrapper fullwidth">
								        
										<p>It&#8217;s finally starting to feel like summer on the East Coast. To wit: the forearms are out, and so are the reading lists. To find out which books everyone is reading and recommending this season (<a href="https://lithub.com/tag/ultimate-summer-reading-list/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">as is my wont</a>), I read 35 summer reading lists from 31 publications, counted up all the books, and tallied them together for you here.</p>
<p>This year, those 35 lists (which are themselves listed at the bottom of this post), recommended a total of 540 individual books. 85 of those appeared on at least 3 lists; those 85 are now presented to you in descending order of popularity. Well, it really speaks for itself, starting with the winner-by-a-mile:</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>19 lists:</strong></p>
<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="247575" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2025/taylor-jenkins-reid-atmosphere-a-love-story/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story-.jpeg" data-orig-size="658,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Taylor Jenkins Reid, Atmosphere- A Love Story" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story--197x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story-.jpeg" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-247575" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story--197x300.jpeg" alt="Taylor Jenkins Reid, Atmosphere- A Love Story" width="197" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story--197x300.jpeg 197w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story--39x60.jpeg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story--33x50.jpeg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Jenkins-Reid-Atmosphere-A-Love-Story-.jpeg 658w" sizes="(max-width: 197px) 100vw, 197px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Taylor Jenkins Reid, <em><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780593158715" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Atmosphere</a></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>15 lists:</strong></p>
<p><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="255423" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-ultimate-summer-2025-reading-list/version-1-0-0-46/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL.jpg" data-orig-size="1500,2280" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Version 1.0.0&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Version 1.0.0&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="s.a. cosby king of ashes" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-197x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-674x1024.jpg" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-255423" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-197x300.jpg" alt="s.a. cosby king of ashes" width="197" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-197x300.jpg 197w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-674x1024.jpg 674w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-768x1167.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-39x60.jpg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-1011x1536.jpg 1011w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-1347x2048.jpg 1347w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/8150S2FjgIL.jpg 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 197px) 100vw, 197px" /></p>
