<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>14 lists:</strong></p>
<p><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="247578" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2025/melissa-febos-the-dry-season-a-memoir-of-pleasure-in-a-year-without-sex/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Melissa-Febos-The-Dry-Season-A-Memoir-of-Pleasure-in-a-Year-Without-Sex-.jpeg" data-orig-size="658,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Melissa Febos, The Dry Season- A Memoir of Pleasure in a Year Without Sex" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Melissa-Febos-The-Dry-Season-A-Memoir-of-Pleasure-in-a-Year-Without-Sex--197x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Melissa-Febos-The-Dry-Season-A-Memoir-of-Pleasure-in-a-Year-Without-Sex-.jpeg" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-247578" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Melissa-Febos-The-Dry-Season-A-Memoir-of-Pleasure-in-a-Year-Without-Sex--197x300.jpeg" alt="Melissa Febos, The Dry Season- A Memoir of Pleasure in a Year Without Sex" width="197" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Melissa-Febos-The-Dry-Season-A-Memoir-of-Pleasure-in-a-Year-Without-Sex--197x300.jpeg 197w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Melissa-Febos-The-Dry-Season-A-Memoir-of-Pleasure-in-a-Year-Without-Sex--39x60.jpeg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Melissa-Febos-The-Dry-Season-A-Memoir-of-Pleasure-in-a-Year-Without-Sex--33x50.jpeg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-co