<p style="text-align: center;">Melissa Febos, <em><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780593537237" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Dry Season</a></em><br />
R.F. Kuang, <em><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063446243" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Katabasis</a></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>13 lists:</strong></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="254747" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/susan-choi-on-writing-a-cross-cultural-story-of-mystery-and-tragedy/flashlight/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight.png" data-orig-size="1333,2000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="flashlight" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-200x300.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-682x1024.png" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-254747" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-200x300.png" alt="" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-200x300.png 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-682x1024.png 682w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-768x1152.png 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-40x60.png 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-1024x1536.png 1024w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight-33x50.png 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/flashlight.png 1333w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></p>
